com.qualcomm.ftccommon.configuration

Enum RequestCode

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<RequestCode>
      • com.qualcomm.ftccommon.configuration.RequestCode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<RequestCode>

    public enum RequestCode
extends java.lang.Enum<RequestCode>
    RequestCode centralizes the integer tokens used for connecting child configuration editors with their parents. The symbolic names of these constants can also appear portions of strings in string or string-array resources in order to be able to connect these integers with display strings suitable for display to humans.
